room_title: Escape room "Licastro’s Lair" by Lincoln Escape Room in Lincoln
review: Had a great time escaping from LiCastros Lair for my sisters birthday! I would recommend this for anyone interested in doing an escape room in the Lincoln Area, especially for bigger parties wanting to work together.

room_title: Escape room "Licastro’s Lair" by Lincoln Escape Room in Lincoln
review: Went with my daughters and our friends to the Escape Room and played LiCastro's Lair. We never knew for sure what we were doing at times, but with 9 seconds left, we won the game. I can't wait to go back and try another room.

room_title: Escape room "Licastro’s Lair" by Lincoln Escape Room in Lincoln
review: Loved everything about the LiCastro Lair. It was just spooky enough, the clues were difficult but in a good way. Highly recommend visiting.
